#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:70
msgid "enum **ShadowCastingSetting**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:72
msgid "**SHADOW_CASTING_SETTING_OFF** = **0** --- Will not cast any shadows."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:74
msgid ""
"**SHADOW_CASTING_SETTING_ON** = **1** --- Will cast shadows from all "
"visible faces in the GeometryInstance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:76
msgid ""
"Will take culling into account, so faces not being rendered will not be "
"taken into account when shadow casting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:78
msgid ""
"**SHADOW_CASTING_SETTING_DOUBLE_SIDED** = **2** --- Will cast shadows "
"from all visible faces in the GeometryInstance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:80
msgid ""
"Will not take culling into account, so all faces will be taken into "
"account when shadow casting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:82
msgid ""
"**SHADOW_CASTING_SETTING_SHADOWS_ONLY** = **3** --- Will only show the "
"shadows casted from this object."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_geometryinstance.rst:84
msgid ""
"In other words, the actual mesh will not be visible, only the shadows "
"casted from the mesh will be."
msgstr ""

